    "2021) C3D A building block called Selective Receptive Fi-eld Convolution (SRFC) is dedicatedly designed and can adaptively adjust its receptive field size according to multiple scales of input information at each temporal location in the feature map -2022 RCL(Wang et al. 2022a) I3D Proposed a continuous anchoring representation method, which unifies and extends existing anchor-based detectors into a continuous regression problem in 2D coordinates - This model is a multi-stage model, and is not the same network model.",
